OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright day today with a mix
OL,6,Fof sunshine and a few showers. Cloud
OL,7,Fwill tend to increase later in the day
OL,8,Fwith perhaps the odd spot of rain
OL,9,Farriving in the south by dusk. Feeling
OL,10,Fpleasant in any sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FOutbreaks of rain will
OL,13,Fcontinue to spread northwards this
OL,14,Fevening, with some heavier bursts
OL,15,Fpossible over the hills. Some drier
OL,16,Fand clearer spells developing during
OL,17,Fthe early hours.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
