OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA band of heavier rain will
OL,6,Fsweep eastwards throughout the
OL,7,Fmorning. Turning brighter into the
OL,8,Fafternoon with a mix of sunshine and a
OL,9,Ffew showers. Blustery, especially near
OL,10,Fthe coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA few
OL,13,Fshowers continuing on Saturday before
OL,14,Fhigh pressure builds giving a largely
OL,15,Fdry and bright Sunday. Monday likely
OL,16,Fto remain dry and bright with
OL,17,Ftemperatures a little above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
